List of required dependencies:

Bcftools (Tools for variant calling and manipulating VCFs and BCFs) Version: 1.6 (using htslib 1.6)
https://samtools.github.io/bcftools/ 

BLAST Command Line Tools 2.7.1+
ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/executables/blast+/LATEST/

BowTie Version 1.2.2
http://bowtie-bio.sourceforge.net/index.shtml

BWA (alignment via Burrows-Wheeler transformation), Version: 0.7.17
http://bio-bwa.sourceforge.net/

CISA Contig Integrator for Sequence Assembly
http://sb.nhri.org.tw/CISA/en/CISA

fasta_split_scaffolds.py - script for splitting fasta sequences by substings of Ns
https://github.com/enormandeau/Scripts

FastQC v0.11.7
https://www.bioinformatics.babraham.ac.uk/projects/fastqc/

Mash version 2.0
https://github.com/marbl/Mash

MultiQC, version 1.5dev
http://multiqc.info/

QUAST, Version: 4.6.1
http://bioinf.spbau.ru/quast

SamTools (Tools for alignments in the SAM format) Version: 1.7
http://samtools.sourceforge.net/

seqtk Version: 1.2
https://github.com/lh3/seqtk

Skesa
TBD

SSPACE BASIC Scaffolding Pre-Assemblies After Contig Extension (SSPACE)
https://github.com/nsoranzo/sspace_basic

SPAdes genome assembler v3.11.1
http://bioinf.spbau.ru/spades

Trimmomatic Version 0.36
http://www.usadellab.org/cms/?page=trimmomatic
